                        <head>No. 144.</head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1876-06-15"><hi rend="italic">June</hi> 15,
                                1876</date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p rend="flushleft"><hi rend="smallcaps">Fish</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington:</hi></p>
                        <p>Informed by detectives Winslow discharged to-day. Brent comes before fall
                            bench Monday.</p>
                        <closer><signed>HOFFMAN.</signed></closer>
